data.description: **Offer Deadline: Monday, July 25th by 5pm.** Owner occupants and investors alike, take note: This two-family checks all your boxes! It may look a raised ranch single-family, but it’s actually a money-making two-family for savvy buyers to check out. Lower level, Unit 1, is a 2BR/1BA with newer wood laminate flooring, a new dishwasher (2022) and vinyl replacement window (2018). Unit 2, is a 3 BR/1BA also with newer floors, updated appliances, and an eat-in kitchen. Units have separate systems (electric baseboard heat), a shared laundry room and a shared back patio, but each unit has its own driveway—two cars can fit tandem in each driveway. Live in one unit and rent the other to pay down your mortgage—great location on a quiet cul-de-sac off Grove St, between Washington and VFW parkway. Close to MBTA bus line, and about 1 mile to West Roxbury Commuter Rail. Stop & Shop, Legacy Place and so much more so close!
